{"tid":1578293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9.29全球反共大遊行將以100%和理非方式遊行！呼籲各國港人響應下列造勢活動！","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T18:34:20.000Z","uid":167548,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a903d00779a3c4abae51c07437e332ed10ddcbf5","tid":1578293,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3iTcV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3iTcV1.jpg&h=5a6a3381&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">10.1國殤</span></strong>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOoPvNb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOoPvNb.jpg&h=28f67e7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一波攻勢： <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港與他國互相揮舞旗幟！呼喚對方</span></strong><br />\n你好難拖一個不表態國家落水, 但是呢家100%拖愛國者落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間：9.23~9.28 每日平均要拉到2~3個國家愛國者落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地點：當地港人決定, 最好是民主象徵地。 香港呢方面再詳談。<br />\n方式：至少一支他國實國旗幟！有心(錢)人可以去買當日旗幟派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;參加者至少要有A4/3/2/1紙"},{"pid":"65d0fb8577c87322ee60b1a6bf938441b720c337","tid":1578293,"uid":117906,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f461e3dc84ffd161a130a1aac4b1e670fd873854","tid":1578293,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"英文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99dde258907c147aa899c3a03bc9db2e0349bf69","tid":1578293,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1c1626a3f2dbb382617f0f3c9d5d94f805a0ba3","tid":1578293,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"各國港人在此報名<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf343a775b245aab859e8258ec9ad1343ef8325","tid":1578293,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1c1626a3f2dbb382617f0f3c9d5d94f805a0ba3","tid":1578293,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"各國港人在此報名<img src=\"/a